but let us examine the Hypothesis in its most splendid form&#xD;<lb/>
in its most defensible form.&#xD;<lb/>
Man is a being compounded of two distinct substances&#xD;<lb/>
Matter &amp; Mind Matter is extensible &amp; divisible&#xD;<lb/>
ergo Mortal Mind is unextended &amp; indivisible ergo&#xD;<lb/>
immortal. The Soul is the Agent which directs the&#xD;<lb/>
Actions of the body which is passive &amp; acts only&#xD;<lb/>
according to the Impulse of the Mind. The body&#xD;<lb/>
is the Medium to convey <add xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">the</add> Sensations <add xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">
