               <unclear>x</unclear>
            </del> are the <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                 rend="strikethrough">
               <unclear>x</unclear>
            </del> Instruments by Which the&#xD;<lb/>
Machine is set in Motion. Reason is the Regulating principle&#xD;<lb/>
by which it is governed. –&#xD;<lb/>
Allowing the existence of a Supreme perfectly good &amp;&#xD;<lb/>
powerful Agent <add xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">in</add> the <add xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">Creating Organized Systems capable of pleasure &amp; pain</add>
