– On Happiness –&#xD;<lb/>
– Definitions –&#xD;<lb/>
1st. The Love of Pleasure &amp; the Aversion to Pain are&#xD;<lb/>
Instinctive Principles impressed on the Human Mind&#xD;<lb/>
from the first Moment of its Existence&#xD;<lb/>
2 They are the Instigating Principles to Action in Man&#xD;<lb/>
3 The Different Modifications of these Principles&#xD;<lb/>
are called Passions –&#xD;<lb/>
4. Reason is the Regulating Principle by which&#xD;<lb/>
the Passions are governed –&#xD;<lb/>
