Man is the Child of Habit&#xD;<lb/>
– Thee I invoke I seek they murky glooms&#xD;<lb/>
– The haunt of wandering ghosts&#xD;<lb/>
light as the pallid lunar <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
