            <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                 rend="strikethrough">Existence which is durable</del> from the Qualities of the Heart&#xD;<lb/>
or from Virtuous or lovely dispositions or shoud there&#xD;<lb/>
be wanting some shadow of them must be present.&#xD;<lb/>
            <unclear xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">9a</unclear> It Can never long dwell in a bad heart or mean&#xD;<lb/>
disposition. <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
