93&#xD;<lb/>
his energies in the greater part of the world.&#xD;<lb/>
will from the general illumination derive&#xD;<lb/>
light to dissipate his errors &amp; to conquer&#xD;<lb/>
his evil passions. Man is fitted for&#xD;<lb/>
Happiness in every Climate &amp; this Happiness&#xD;<lb/>
is ultimately to be acquired from Knowledge&#xD;<lb/>
Wisdom &amp; Virtue –&#xD;<lb/>
