98&#xD;<lb/>
Excess of Cold or Heat seem to destroy the Energies of&#xD;<lb/>
the Green lander &amp; the <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                xml:id="ttag126"
