               <term xml:id="tag126">
          Hottentot
        </term>
            </rs> are alike &#xD;<lb/>
ignorant stupid <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                 rend="strikethrough">&amp;</del> <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
