            <lb/>
Nature has <add xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">largely</add> bestowed her bounties upon warm Counties&#xD;<lb/>
&amp; provided for that Indolence which the heat&#xD;<lb/>
Climat must naturally <add xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">(necessarily)</add> induce –&#xD;<lb/>
The Nations between the tropics are not only distinguished&#xD;<lb/>
            <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
