99&#xD;<lb/>
sublime Theories.&#xD;<lb/>
* Indeed the Sciences in the East seem to&#xD;<lb/>
have been confined to a Class of Men&#xD;<lb/>
namely the Priests in whom the Strongest&#xD;<lb/>
moral Motives namely Ambition &amp;&#xD;<lb/>
a desire to enslave Mankind, called forth&#xD;<lb/>
all the Energies of the Mind &amp; overcame&#xD;<lb/>
the Influence of Climat –&#xD;<lb/>
The Common people in Asia &amp; <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                xml:id="ttag128"
