111&#xD;<lb/>
This Imperfection cannot be attributed to Moral Causes.&#xD;<lb/>
The Greenlanders have no laws &amp; scarcely any Religion&#xD;<lb/>
The Swedish Laplanders are under a free government&#xD;<lb/>
