            <lb/>
To determine the Influence of Climat on Man&#xD;<lb/>
it is necessary to take a view of the different&#xD;<lb/>
Regions of the Earth, to mark the Peculiarities&#xD;<lb/>
of evey climate &amp; the Manners of the Inhabitants&#xD;<lb/>
To consider what is the <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
