An Essay on the Influence of Climate on National&#xD;<lb/>
Manners &amp; Character. –&#xD;<lb/>
We discover not only in every Nation, but almost in every&#xD;<lb/>
Province, a difference of Manners &amp; Character &amp; this&#xD;<lb/>
