                 rend="strikethrough">different</del> &amp; even different provinces&#xD;<lb/>
of the Same Kingdom where the same laws &amp; customs prevail <add xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">dissimilar in their Manners</add>
