of Manners &amp; Character. People under the same government&#xD;<lb/>
Professing the same Religion &amp; educated in the same manner.&#xD;<lb/>
are found to be very different in their Manners &amp; Character&#xD;<lb/>
But this difference is more distinguishable in People of&#xD;<lb/>
different &amp; Remote Countries. The Influence of Religious&#xD;<lb/>
