132&#xD;<lb/>
The Influence of Climate on National Manners&#xD;<lb/>
and Character&#xD;<lb/>
1 The Greenlanders are ignorant dull &amp; phlegmatic&#xD;<lb/>
living without laws. they live peaceably &amp; preserve&#xD;<lb/>
good order.&#xD;<lb/>
2 The Laplanders are strong &amp; active of short Stature&#xD;<lb/>
Timorous hasty &amp; Passionate&#xD;<lb/>
3 The Norwegians are descended from the Normans.&#xD;<lb/>
Robust hardy &amp; well made honest hospitable&#xD;<lb/>
brave honest &amp; <unclear xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">xxxxxxxxx courageous but xxxxxx</unclear>
