fond of Music&#xD;<lb/>
The Swedes are strong <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                 rend="strikethrough">active</del> &amp; Robust. inactive their&#xD;<lb/>
Mental faculties very imperfect dul of apprehension&#xD;<lb/>
with Narrow Capacities.&#xD;<lb/>
Russians ignorant brutal have but imperfect&#xD;<lb/>
Notions of the social Virtues –&#xD;<lb/>
The Chinese are ceremonious to the Extreme in a great&#xD;<lb/>
degree polite &amp; in some measure hospitable&#xD;<lb/>
They behave with much respect to each other&#xD;<lb/>
&amp; to strangers, treat their Parents with affect<hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="superscript">n</hi>
            <lb/>
&amp; Their Women with decency&#xD;<lb/>
The air is cold in the Northern parts but in&#xD;<lb/>
the Southern part is extremely sultry&#xD;<lb/>
but the air of the greater part of the Empire&#xD;<lb/>
is temperate serene &amp; salubrious&#xD;<lb/>
